{"tid":1685824,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多圖mk紋身妹 多圖呀","createTime":"2019-10-31T19:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T17:52:23.000Z","uid":64819,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a992b89bba4c0576e6abfe61778f5fc13d518bd7","tid":1685824,"uid":64819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:06:56.000Z","msg":"事源是咁的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友就係間ig shop諗住買鞋 就已經比左訂 然後尾數想面交。<br />\n咁店主一直話自己好忙 要比埋尾數先可以面交 <br />\n朋友就要求店主影實物相出黎 <br />\n店主就影左一對size完全唔啱嘅鞋出黎 朋友一睇個size就心知不妙 即刻要睇張單 <br />\n然後個店主一直多多嗲話影唔到又剩 又唔肯退錢 <br />\n然後經過一番周轉 店主先死死地氣咁退錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你身冇屎 洗乜一拎你啲相出嚟即刻縮曬水退錢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUWPoFx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUWPoFx.jpg&h=1019dc22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdwjLT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkdwjLT1.jpg&h=58e7b2a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRCKW0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRCKW0J.jpg&h=99117550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n店主本人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WhB0vkZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhB0vkZ.jpg&h=563dbb6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rjxmsE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rjxmsE.jpg&h=80584d65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cG7ZLUk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcG7ZLUk.jpg&h=ae9e8c08&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxkXxzm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxkXxzm.jpg&h=f7a42ee8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/01/025424_4a4edfcb5a9914a23af7f18523773391.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F01%2F025424_4a4edfcb5a9914a23af7f18523773391.jpeg&h=e15b25f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/01/025425_ae4be30c0e3be97108de8d621b5d7bd1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F01%2F025425_ae4be30c0e3be97108de8d621b5d7bd1.jpeg&h=a99f586b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/01/025425_f92dd572af6c43d7bf72239006bc2a78.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F01%2F025425_f92dd572af6c43d7bf72239006bc2a78.jpeg&h=b413877d&s={SIZE}\" />睇下個紋身幾性感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁撚索唔係唔加人地fb吹水下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後經過我朋友一翻事件後 我醒起半年前都係佢度買過兩對鞋 就拿拿林搵翻當初張單出黎對 唔睇都冇事 一睇 哇我屌 根本就貨不對品！((其實係我蠢 收到鞋後冇仔細對單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我話粗粗膽地問佢可否退單 點知<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ekMcmuD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FekMcmuD.png&h=9d67bb15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n勇氣可嘉 你以為我唔知海關咩效率咩 大我呀mk妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fiL8Eho.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfiL8Eho.png&h=e479a588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家小心啲呢啲間呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nig : <a href=\"http://whatsize.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatsize.hk&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=106aaf87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">whatsize.hk</a><br />\nfb : suki suen<br />\n電話 